sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Client as App Cliente
    participant Token as /api/auth/token
    participant Hosted as HostedAuthenticationAppService
    participant Master as SaasMasterDb
    participant Users as tenant_{id}.Users
    participant Issuer as Tenant JWT Issuer
    participant Discovery as /tenants/{tenantId}/.well-known
    participant Api as API Protegida

    Client->>Token: POST /api/auth/token + X-Tenant-Id + grant_type=authorization_code
    Token->>Hosted: ExchangeAuthorizationCodeAsync
    Hosted->>Master: Consumir AuthorizationCodeGrant por tenant, client, redirect_uri e PKCE
    Hosted->>Users: Recarregar usuário, status e roles
    Hosted->>Issuer: Emitir JWT tenant-scoped e refresh token
    Token-->>Client: AuthTokenResponse token(access_token, refresh_token)

    Client->>Api: Request com Bearer access_token
    Api->>Discovery: GET /tenants/{tenantId}/.well-known/openid-configuration
    Discovery-->>Api: issuer do tenant + jwks_uri
    Api->>Discovery: GET /tenants/{tenantId}/.well-known/jwks.json
    Discovery-->>Api: Chave pública RSA do tenant
    Api->>Api: Validar assinatura, issuer, audience, exp, roles/scopes e tenantId
    Api-->>Client: Recurso autorizado
